#Text=The Boston Celtics ( 8 - 7 ) defeated the Philadelphia 76ers ( 0 - 16 ) 84 - 80 on Wednesday in yet another late - game collapse for Philly . .
#Text=The Sixers played very well in this game , but choked it away late to extend their horrible losing - streak .
#Text=The Celtics ended the game on an 18 - 3 run over the last six minutes and that 's the Sixers season in a nutshell .
#Text=Both teams shot poorly in this game , as they both shot below 38 percent from the field .
#Text=This definitely was n't a pretty game by any means , but Boston fans will be happy that they were n't the ones to allow that first elusive win to the Sixers .
#Text=The Sixers usually lose games early , but when it 's close at the end , they do n't know how to finish games either .
#Text=It 's a sad reality for a team in a deep hole , but losses like these still have to be looked at positively .
#Text=They were ahead for the majority of the second half and it was still one of their best performances of the year , despite the loss .
#Text=Jahlil Okafor once again led the team in scoring , as he tallied 19 points and 11 rebounds in the defeat .
#Text=He is definitely a major bright spot in a dark tunnel and Philly fans can be somewhat hopeful for the future with his strong play this season .
#Text=Philadelphia will look to crack this losing - streak when they take on the struggling Houston Rockets on Friday .
#Text=The Celtics played poorly on Wednesday , but somehow escaped with a win .
#Text=Only two Boston players scored more than 10 points in this game and they were lucky to grab a win in such a poor performance .
#Text=Despite the struggles , Isaiah Thomas had a great game , totaling 30 points , six assists and four rebounds in the victory .
#Text=Evan Turner also had a nice game off the bench , as he collected 16 points , nine rebounds and three assists .
#Text=Jared Sullinger also snatched 15 boards , so it was n't all bad for Boston .
#Text=The gritty nature to go on a big run and pull out a win like this late can be a huge momentum booster for a young team .

#Text=They 'll host a Washington Wizards team on Friday , who are coming off one of the biggest chokes of the season as well , as they scored six points in the fourth quarter in Wednesday 's loss to the Charlotte Hornets . .
